videos.description: Gabby Williams with the quick bounce pass sets up Napheesa Collier for the score.
videos.headline: Williams bounces pass perfectly to Collier for UConn bucket

videos.description: Kate Lou Samuelson draws the double-team then passes over to a wide open Napheesa Collier who lays it in.
videos.headline: UConn's Collier left open for easy score.

videos.description: Gabby Williams gets the steal and passes down court to Katie Lou Samuelson who lays in the uncontested bucket.
videos.headline: Williams steal sets up Samuelson fast-break layup

videos.description: Geno Auriemma is visibly happy with the Kia Nurse's wide open 3-pointer from the wing.
videos.headline: Nurse's 3-pointer leaves Geno smiling

videos.description: Connecticut's Kia Nurse is left open in the corner off the inbounds pass and easily makes the uncontested 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Nurse knocks down open 3-pointer

videos.description: In a matchup of top-10 teams, Kia Nurse and Katie Lou Samuelson combine to score 43 points as No. 1 Connecticut routs No. 7 South Carolina 83-58.
videos.headline: UConn dominates South Carolina
